        {% comment %} ── HIGHLIGHTED COMBO SELECTION AREA (APP + VARIANTS) ── {% endcomment %}
        <div class="fit11-main-action-btns" id="fit11MainBtnContainer">

          {% comment %} ── NEW OFFERS & DISCOUNTS SECTION (MOVED ABOVE APP BLOCK) ── {% endcomment %}
