              <p style="margin-bottom: 16px; color: var(--lux-text);">Items purchased from 11fit are eligible for return/exchange, if returned within 7 days of delivery.</p>

              <p style="margin-bottom: 4px; font-weight: 600; color: var(--lux-text);">Free Exchanges</p>
              <p style="margin-bottom: 16px; color: var(--lux-text-muted);">We accept exchanges free of cost. This means you won't be charged extra to exchange the product(s). It's on us! We want your experience to be hassle-free.</p>

              <p style="margin-bottom: 4px; font-weight: 600; color: var(--lux-text);">Easy Returns</p>
